==English==

===Etymology===
From the ''[[w:Star Trek|Star Trek]]'' franchise, purportedly by Gene Roddenberry, named for Lieutenant Wilbur Clingan of the Los Angeles Police Department

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|klĭng'ŏn}}, {{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɒn/|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɑn/|/ˈkliŋɑn/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|countable}} Member of a fictional [[alien]] warrior [[race]] depicted as having distinctive forehead [[ridge]]s and a [[culture]] based on strict observance of [[honour]], [[loyalty]], and [[combat]].

